@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
[*] --> Created
Created --> Delivered : update
Delivered --> Closed : approve
Delivered : entry / log notification
Closed --> Completed : reject
Closed : entry / log notification
Completed --> Cancelled : confirm
Cancelled --> Rejected : confirm
Rejected --> [*]
@enduml